    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1895-05-20T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1895-05-20T00:00:00-05:00" n="473" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d473">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Taylor</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Madrid</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-05-20">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 20,
                                1895</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Interview with the minister for foreign affairs. Presented demand. He
                            said he had no knowledge of the case, but promised to communicate with
                            Cuba at once, in order to answer as soon as possible.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Taylor.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
